#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.49"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.49:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.49:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga"
msgstr "5. The Deathless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.49:0.3"
msgid "49. Vedanāsutta"
msgstr "49. Feelings"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.49:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, vedanā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three feelings."

msgctxt "sn47.49:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn47.49:1.3"
msgid "Sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā—"
msgstr "Pleasant, painful, and neutral feeling."

msgctxt "sn47.49:1.4"
msgid "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso vedanā."
msgstr "These are the three feelings."

msgctxt "sn47.49:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ vedanānaṃ pariññāya cattāro satipaṭṭhānā "
"bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"The four kinds of mindfulness meditation should be developed to completely "
"understand these three feelings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.49:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.49:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.49:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.49:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.49:2.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.49:2.6"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ vedanānaṃ pariññāya ime cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhānā bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These four kinds of mindfulness meditation should be developed to completely "
"understand these three feelings.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.49:2.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
